Choreo CHALLENGE

A choreo challenge is an intensive training program, created for all the dancers who want to challenge themselves and bring their dancing to the performance level.

It’s also about making friends and sharing your passion with a motivated team. Being proud of what you accomplished and having the opportunity to perform in front of more than 2000 people!

Learn a choreography in 10 hours and show your work on stage on Sunday night at PISC!

For each bootcamp we accept max 30 participants. Be sure to book your choreo challenge pass as soon as possible.

KAREL FLORES / USA
LADIES WITH STYLE



SERGIO & BIANCA / MEXICO
FOR BACHATA LOVERS



Do not miss this opportunity. The body movement, the musicality, the arms style, turn technique, everything will be examined closely.

To allow you to perfect and to reach the top you will be coached by one of the best dancers choreographer of the planet salsa, Karel Flores alias «Flower Power».

Here you have the chance to receive a professional coaching by Sergio & Bianca coming to us from Mexico and members of the famous company multiple champion of Bachata, "Alma Latina".

Raise the challenge and perform on stage in their side. Sensation guaranteed!
